  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/c153c630918efad407d0f62a49282a3f.avif?t=1745583717\" width=600 height=179 /></span><br>Alien Breakout is a precision platformer where you control an alien that has been captured and must escape from the laboratory. Throughout your adventure, you will acquire a weapon to defeat enemies, and various mechanics will be introduced in each level.<br><br><strong>⮞ Grab your weapon and escape the lab</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/dea7d402fd0dd5fb8c50ebba8f072b42.poster.avif?t=1745583717\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/dea7d402fd0dd5fb8c50ebba8f072b42.webm?t=1745583717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/dea7d402fd0dd5fb8c50ebba8f072b42.mp4?t=1745583717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>⮞ Watch out for the guards!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/364ca5bac18b87d27711a442b7779688.poster.avif?t=1745583717\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/364ca5bac18b87d27711a442b7779688.webm?t=1745583717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/364ca5bac18b87d27711a442b7779688.mp4?t=1745583717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>⮞ Be quick and face the enemies</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/3fb5bedc46986f75e7ca560c417affa6.poster.avif?t=1745583717\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/3fb5bedc46986f75e7ca560c417affa6.webm?t=1745583717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581220/extras/3fb5bedc46986f75e7ca560c417affa6.mp4?t=1745583717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
